Enclosing class:
METASCHEMA
@MetaschemaAssembly(formalName="Global Assembly Definition", description="In XML, an element with structured element content. In JSON, an object with properties. Defined globally, an assembly can be assigned to appear in the `model` of any assembly (another assembly type, or itself), by `assembly` reference.", name="define-assembly", moduleClass=MetaschemaModelModule.class) public static class METASCHEMA.DefineAssembly extends Object implements IBoundObject
In XML, an element with structured element content. In JSON, an object with properties. Defined globally, an assembly can be assigned to appear in the model of any assembly (another assembly type, or itself), by assembly reference.
